data.description: This absolutely gorgeous home has many updates and renovations to include new flooring throughout the property.  This home has been beautifully maintained. Home features a chef kitchen to include 8 gas burners, bulit-in fryer, center hood, large pantry and utility room, a theater room with projector and automatic large screen, sunrooms, exercise room, deck on each level of the home.  Large spacious living area featuring a large fireplace and big windows that provide views of the city and surrounding neighborhoods.  Each bedroom features a living area and balcony. There is a nice in-ground pool and Koi pond in the beautiful, landscaped backyard.  There is a pool house, wine room, built in fish tank. weight room, the master bedroom has very large walk-in closets that are absolutely amazing, office, foyer. This home is a must see.
